{"id":232738757,"title":"港口","content":"走了太遠，忘記了原路。走了太久，夜晚發現了回憶，你忘記了來去的人。走了太長，你已忘記時間，悄悄的流逝。\n我們都祈願著，在這廣闊的世界中，能有你停留的港口，不再飄泊。\n所以，港口呢？\n在哪？我停在半路上，問著。\n\n遠方的聲音回著，再繼續往前走吧。","excerpt":"走了太遠，忘記了原路。走了太久，夜晚發現了回憶，你忘記了來去的人。走了太長，你已忘記時間，悄悄的流逝。我們都祈願著，在這廣闊的世界中，能有你停留的港口，不再飄泊。所以，港口呢？在哪？我停在半路上，問著","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":false,"pinned":false,"forumId":"f8acd3e6-17e9-4d9d-bc7c-bf24d94c2ad1","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-12-22T13:07:32.088Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-22T13:07:32.088Z","commentCount":2,"likeCount":1,"tags":["HIDE_THUMBNAIL"],"topics":["心情","文字","日常","感情","隨筆"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":true,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"詩文","forumAlias":"literature","school":"貓女子","department":"g_catgirl","replyTitle":null,"gender":"F","personaSubscriptable":true,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":1}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":false,"withVideos":false,"media":[],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[],"postAvatar":""}